              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "CaCl2 foil target, enriched to >98% 37Cl, and about",
                " 90 mg/cm**2 thick, placed between 25-mg/cm**2 Ca foil.",
                "The large difference (13.5 MeV) in (p,n) Q-value",
                " between the 40Ca and 37Cl nuclei permits a clean",
                " observation of low-lying states in 37Ar.",
                "A second target, 32.2 mg/cm**2 of CaCl2 with aluminized",
                " mylar as protective layers, was also used to obtain a",
                " cross check on the absolute cross section values."
              ]
            }
          ],
